@* Dialog لإدارة كل البنود اليدوية على الراتب قبل الإرسال للمراجعة *@
@using COCOBOLOERPNEW.DTOs
@using MudBlazor

@inject ISnackbar Snackbar

<MudDialog>
    <TitleContent>
        <div class="d-flex align-center gap-2">
            <MudIcon Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Tune" Color="Color.Primary" />
            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">إدارة بنود راتب @_editCalc.EmployeeName</MudText>
        </div>
    </TitleContent>

    <DialogContent>
        <MudGrid Spacing="2">

            @* ── ملخص سريع ── *@
            <MudItem xs="12">
                <MudPaper Class="pa-3 rounded-xl" Style="background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">
                    <MudGrid Spacing="1">
                        <MudItem xs="6" md="3">
                            <MudText Typo="Typo.caption">الأساسي</MudText>
                            <MudText><b>@_editCalc.BasicSalary.ToString("N2") جـ</b></MudText>
                        </MudItem>
                        <MudItem xs="6" md="3">
                            <MudText Typo="Typo.caption">أيام الحضور</MudText>
                            <MudText><b>@_editCalc.PresentDays / @_editCalc.WorkingDaysInMonth</b></MudText>
                        </MudItem>
                        <MudItem xs="6" md="3">
                            <MudText Typo="Typo.caption">الغياب</MudText>
                            <MudText Color="Color.Error"><b>@_editCalc.AbsenceDays يوم</b></MudText>
                        </MudItem>
                        <MudItem xs="6" md="3">
                            <MudText Typo="Typo.caption">التأخير</MudText>
                            <MudText Color="Color.Warning"><b>@_editCalc.LateDisplay</b></MudText>
                        </MudItem>
                    </MudGrid>
                </MudPaper>
            </MudItem>

            @* ── الخصومات الآلية القابلة للتعديل ── *@
            <MudItem xs="12">
                <MudPaper Class="pa-3 rounded-xl" Style="border:1px solid #fee2e2;background:#fff7f7;">
                    <div class="d-flex align-center justify-space-between mb-2">
                        <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1" Color="Color.Error"><b>الخصومات الآلية القابلة للتعديل</b></MudText>
                    </div>
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.caption" Color="Color.Secondary" Class="mb-3 d-block">
                        يمكنك تعديل خصم الغياب وخصم التأخير يدويًا عند الحاجة مع كتابة سبب التعديل. خصم السلفة للقراءة فقط ويتم التحكم فيه من شاشة السلف.
                    </MudText>

                    <MudGrid Spacing="2">
                        <MudItem xs="12" md="4">
                            <MudText Typo="Typo.caption">خصم الغياب المحسوب آليًا</MudText>
                            <MudText Color="Color.Error"><b>@_originalAbsenceDeduction.ToString("N2") جـ</b></MudText>
                        </MudItem>
                        <MudItem xs="12" md="4">
                            <MudNumericField T="decimal"
                                             @bind-Value="_editCalc.AbsenceDeduction"
                                             Label="خصم الغياب النهائي"
                                             Min="0"
                                             Variant="Variant.Outlined"
                                             Margin="Margin.Dense" />
                        </MudItem>
                        <MudItem xs="12" md="4">
                            <MudTextField T="string"
                                          @bind-Value="_absenceOverrideReason"
                                          Label="سبب تعديل الغياب"
                                          Variant="Variant.Outlined"
                                          Margin="Margin.Dense" />
                        </MudItem>

                        <MudItem xs="12" md="4">
                            <MudText Typo="Typo.caption">خصم التأخير المحسوب آليًا</MudText>
                            <MudText Color="Color.Error"><b>@_originalLateDeduction.ToString("N2") جـ</b></MudText>
                        </MudItem>
                        <MudItem xs="12" md="4">
                            <MudNumericField T="decimal"
                                             @bind-Value="_editCalc.LateDeduction"
                                             Label="خصم التأخير النهائي"
                                             Min="0"
                                             Variant="Variant.Outlined"
                                             Margin="Margin.Dense" />
                        </MudItem>
                        <MudItem xs="12" md="4">
                            <MudTextField T="string"
                                          @bind-Value="_lateOverrideReason"
                                          Label="سبب تعديل التأخير"
                                          Variant="Variant.Outlined"
                                          Margin="Margin.Dense" />
                        </MudItem>

                        <MudItem xs="12" md="4">
                            <MudText Typo="Typo.caption">خصم السلفة</MudText>
                            <MudText Color="Color.Error"><b>@_originalLoanDeduction.ToString("N2") جـ</b></MudText>
                        </MudItem>
                        <MudItem xs="12" md="8">
                            <MudAlert Severity="Severity.Info" Dense="true" Variant="Variant.Outlined" Class="mb-0">
                                خصم السلفة للعرض فقط. إذا كنت تحتاج تأجيل أو تعديل قسط السلفة، يتم ذلك من موديول السلف وليس من شاشة الرواتب.
                            </MudAlert>
                        </MudItem>
                    </MudGrid>
                </MudPaper>
            </MudItem>

            @* ── خصومات يدوية وجزاءات ── *@
            <MudItem xs="12">
                <div class="d-flex align-center justify-space-between mb-2">
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle2" Color="Color.Error">🔴 خصومات يدوية وجزاءات</MudText>
                    <MudIconButton Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Add"
                                   Size="Size.Small"
                                   Color="Color.Error"
                                   OnClick="AddPenalty" />
                </div>
                <MudText Typo="Typo.caption" Color="Color.Secondary" Class="mb-2 d-block">
                    استخدم هذا الجزء لأي خصم يدوي أو جزاء إداري إضافي لهذا الشهر.
                </MudText>

                @foreach (var (item, idx) in _editCalc.Penalties.Select((x, i) => (x, i)))
                {
                    <MudPaper Class="pa-2 mb-1 rounded-lg d-flex gap-2 align-center flex-wrap"
                              Style="border:1px solid #fee2e2">
                        <MudSelect T="string" @bind-Value="item.DetailType" Variant="Variant.Text" Margin="Margin.Dense" Style="min-width:140px">
                            <MudSelectItem T="string" Value="@("Penalty")">جزاء</MudSelectItem>
                            <MudSelectItem T="string" Value="@("ManualDeduction")">خصم يدوي</MudSelectItem>
                        </MudSelect>
                        <MudTextField @bind-Value="item.Description"
                                      Placeholder="وصف الخصم أو الجزاء"
                                      Variant="Variant.Text"
                                      Margin="Margin.Dense"
                                      Style="flex:1" />
                        <MudNumericField T="decimal"
                                         @bind-Value="item.Amount"
                                         Placeholder="المبلغ"
                                         Variant="Variant.Text"
                                         Margin="Margin.Dense"
                                         Min="0"
                                         Style="max-width:120px" />
                        <MudText>جـ</MudText>
                        <MudIconButton Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Delete"
                                       Size="Size.Small" Color="Color.Error"
                                       OnClick="@(() => _editCalc.Penalties.RemoveAt(idx))" />
                    </MudPaper>
                }
                @if (!_editCalc.Penalties.Any())
                {
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.caption" Color="Color.Secondary">لا توجد خصومات/جزاءات يدوية</MudText>
                }
            </MudItem>

            @* ── إضافات داخل الراتب ── *@
            <MudItem xs="12">
                <div class="d-flex align-center justify-space-between mb-2">
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle2" Color="Color.Success">🟢 إضافات داخل الراتب</MudText>
                    <MudIconButton Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Add"
                                   Size="Size.Small" Color="Color.Success"
                                   OnClick="AddBonus" />
                </div>
                <MudText Typo="Typo.caption" Color="Color.Secondary" Class="mb-2 d-block">
                    هذه البنود تُضاف مباشرة إلى صافي الراتب وتدخل ضمن إجمالي المرتب الشهري.
                </MudText>

                @foreach (var (item, idx) in _editCalc.BonusItems.Select((x, i) => (x, i)))
                {
                    <MudPaper Class="pa-2 mb-1 rounded-lg d-flex gap-2 align-center flex-wrap"
                              Style="border:1px solid #dcfce7">
                        <MudSelect T="string" @bind-Value="item.DetailType" Variant="Variant.Text" Margin="Margin.Dense" Style="min-width:140px">
                            <MudSelectItem T="string" Value="@("Bonus")">مكافأة</MudSelectItem>
                            <MudSelectItem T="string" Value="@("Commission")">عمولة</MudSelectItem>
                        </MudSelect>
                        <MudTextField @bind-Value="item.Description"
                                      Placeholder="وصف الإضافة"
                                      Variant="Variant.Text"
                                      Margin="Margin.Dense"
                                      Style="flex:1" />
                        <MudNumericField T="decimal"
                                         @bind-Value="item.Amount"
                                         Placeholder="المبلغ"
                                         Variant="Variant.Text"
                                         Margin="Margin.Dense"
                                         Min="0"
                                         Style="max-width:120px" />
                        <MudText>جـ</MudText>
                        <MudIconButton Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Delete"
                                       Size="Size.Small" Color="Color.Error"
                                       OnClick="@(() => _editCalc.BonusItems.RemoveAt(idx))" />
                    </MudPaper>
                }
                @if (!_editCalc.BonusItems.Any())
                {
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.caption" Color="Color.Secondary">
                        لا توجد إضافات داخل الراتب
                    </MudText>
                }
            </MudItem>

            @* ── إضافات خارج الراتب ── *@
            <MudItem xs="12">
                <div class="d-flex align-center justify-space-between mb-2">
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle2" Color="Color.Info">🔵 مكافآت منفصلة (خارج الراتب)</MudText>
                    <MudIconButton Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Add"
                                   Size="Size.Small" Color="Color.Info"
                                   OnClick="AddSeparateBonus" />
                </div>
                <MudText Typo="Typo.caption" Color="Color.Secondary" Class="mb-2 d-block">
                    هذه البنود لا تدخل في صافي الراتب، لكنها تُصرف كحركة خزينة مستقلة عند الصرف الفردي أو الجماعي.
                </MudText>

                @foreach (var (item, idx) in _editCalc.SeparateBonuses.Select((x, i) => (x, i)))
                {
                    <MudPaper Class="pa-2 mb-1 rounded-lg d-flex gap-2 align-center flex-wrap"
                              Style="border:1px solid #dbeafe">
                        <MudSelect T="string" @bind-Value="item.DetailType" Variant="Variant.Text" Margin="Margin.Dense" Style="min-width:160px">
                            <MudSelectItem T="string" Value="@("BonusSeparate")">مكافأة منفصلة</MudSelectItem>
                            <MudSelectItem T="string" Value="@("CommissionSeparate")">عمولة منفصلة</MudSelectItem>
                        </MudSelect>
                        <MudTextField @bind-Value="item.Description"
                                      Placeholder="وصف المكافأة المنفصلة"
                                      Variant="Variant.Text"
                                      Margin="Margin.Dense"
                                      Style="flex:1" />
                        <MudNumericField T="decimal"
                                         @bind-Value="item.Amount"
                                         Placeholder="المبلغ"
                                         Variant="Variant.Text"
                                         Margin="Margin.Dense"
                                         Min="0"
                                         Style="max-width:120px" />
                        <MudText>جـ</MudText>
                        <MudIconButton Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Delete"
                                       Size="Size.Small" Color="Color.Error"
                                       OnClick="@(() => _editCalc.SeparateBonuses.RemoveAt(idx))" />
                    </MudPaper>
                }
                @if (!_editCalc.SeparateBonuses.Any())
                {
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.caption" Color="Color.Secondary">
                        لا توجد إضافات منفصلة
                    </MudText>
                }
            </MudItem>

            @* ── الملخص النهائي ── *@
            <MudItem xs="12">
                <MudPaper Class="pa-3 rounded-xl" Style="background:#f0fdf4;border:2px solid #10b981">
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1" Color="Color.Success">
                        الصافي النهائي داخل الراتب: <b>@_editCalc.NetSalary.ToString("N2") جـ</b>
                    </MudText>
                    @if (_editCalc.TotalSeparateBonuses > 0)
                    {
                        <MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Color="Color.Info">
                            + إضافات خارج الراتب: @_editCalc.TotalSeparateBonuses.ToString("N2") جـ
                        </MudText>
                    }
                    @if (_editCalc.AbsenceDeduction != _originalAbsenceDeduction || _editCalc.LateDeduction != _originalLateDeduction)
                    {
                        <MudText Typo="Typo.caption" Color="Color.Secondary">
                            تم تعديل الخصومات الآلية يدويًا لهذه المعالجة وسيتم حفظ السبب داخل ملاحظات الراتب للمراجعة.
                        </MudText>
                    }
                </MudPaper>
            </MudItem>
        </MudGrid>
    </DialogContent>

    <DialogActions>
        <MudButton OnClick="Cancel" Variant="Variant.Text">إلغاء</MudButton>
        <MudButton OnClick="Save"
                   Variant="Variant.Filled"
                   Color="Color.Primary"
                   StartIcon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Check">
            تأكيد
        </MudButton>
    </DialogActions>
</MudDialog>

@code {
    [CascadingParameter] public IMudDialogInstance MudDialog { get; set; } = null!;
    [Parameter] public PayrollCalculationDto Calc { get; set; } = null!;
    [Parameter] public EventCallback OnSaved { get; set; }

    private PayrollCalculationDto _editCalc = new();
    private decimal _originalAbsenceDeduction;
    private decimal _originalLateDeduction;
    private decimal _originalLoanDeduction;
    private string? _absenceOverrideReason;
    private string? _lateOverrideReason;

    protected override void OnParametersSet()
    {
        if (Calc is null) return;

        _originalAbsenceDeduction = Calc.AutoAbsenceDeduction > 0 || Calc.AbsenceDeduction == 0
            ? Calc.AutoAbsenceDeduction
            : Calc.AbsenceDeduction;
        _originalLateDeduction = Calc.AutoLateDeduction > 0 || Calc.LateDeduction == 0
            ? Calc.AutoLateDeduction
            : Calc.LateDeduction;
        _originalLoanDeduction = Calc.LoanDeduction;

        _editCalc = new PayrollCalculationDto
        {
            EmployeeID = Calc.EmployeeID,
            EmployeeName = Calc.EmployeeName,
            Department = Calc.Department,
            BasicSalary = Calc.BasicSalary,
            WorkingDaysInMonth = Calc.WorkingDaysInMonth,
            PresentDays = Calc.PresentDays,
            AbsenceDays = Calc.AbsenceDays,
            LateMinutesTotal = Calc.LateMinutesTotal,
            IsManualAttendance = Calc.IsManualAttendance,
            AutoAbsenceDeduction = Calc.AutoAbsenceDeduction > 0 || Calc.AbsenceDeduction == 0
                ? Calc.AutoAbsenceDeduction
                : Calc.AbsenceDeduction,
            AutoLateDeduction = Calc.AutoLateDeduction > 0 || Calc.LateDeduction == 0
                ? Calc.AutoLateDeduction
                : Calc.LateDeduction,
            AbsenceDeduction = Calc.AbsenceDeduction,
            LateDeduction = Calc.LateDeduction,
            LoanDeduction = Calc.LoanDeduction,
            AbsenceOverrideReason = Calc.AbsenceOverrideReason,
            LateOverrideReason = Calc.LateOverrideReason,
            HasExistingPayroll = Calc.HasExistingPayroll,
            ExistingPayrollID = Calc.ExistingPayrollID,
            Warning = Calc.Warning,
            IsSelected = Calc.IsSelected,
            LoanItems = Calc.LoanItems.Select(x => CloneDetail(x)).ToList(),
            Penalties = Calc.Penalties.Select(x => CloneDetail(x)).ToList(),
            BonusItems = Calc.BonusItems.Select(x => CloneDetail(x)).ToList(),
            SeparateBonuses = Calc.SeparateBonuses.Select(x => CloneDetail(x)).ToList()
        };

        _absenceOverrideReason = Calc.AbsenceOverrideReason;
        _lateOverrideReason = Calc.LateOverrideReason;
    }

    private static PayrollDetailDto CloneDetail(PayrollDetailDto x) => new()
    {
        DetailID = x.DetailID,
        DetailType = x.DetailType,
        Description = x.Description,
        Amount = x.Amount,
        IsDeduction = x.IsDeduction,
        PaymentType = x.PaymentType,
        Notes = x.Notes
    };

    private void AddPenalty() => _editCalc.Penalties.Add(new PayrollDetailDto
    {
        DetailType = "Penalty",
        IsDeduction = true,
        PaymentType = "InPayroll"
    });

    private void AddBonus() => _editCalc.BonusItems.Add(new PayrollDetailDto
    {
        DetailType = "Bonus",
        IsDeduction = false,
        PaymentType = "InPayroll"
    });

    private void AddSeparateBonus() => _editCalc.SeparateBonuses.Add(new PayrollDetailDto
    {
        DetailType = "BonusSeparate",
        IsDeduction = false,
        PaymentType = "Separate"
    });

    private async Task Save()
    {
        _editCalc.Penalties.RemoveAll(p => p.Amount <= 0 || string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(p.Description));
        _editCalc.BonusItems.RemoveAll(b => b.Amount <= 0 || string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(b.Description));
        _editCalc.SeparateBonuses.RemoveAll(b => b.Amount <= 0 || string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(b.Description));

        if (_editCalc.AbsenceDeduction != _originalAbsenceDeduction && string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(_absenceOverrideReason))
        {
            Snackbar.Add("اكتب سبب تعديل خصم الغياب قبل الحفظ", Severity.Warning);
            return;
        }

        if (_editCalc.LateDeduction != _originalLateDeduction && string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(_lateOverrideReason))
        {
            Snackbar.Add("اكتب سبب تعديل خصم التأخير قبل الحفظ", Severity.Warning);
            return;
        }

        Calc.AutoAbsenceDeduction = _editCalc.AutoAbsenceDeduction;
        Calc.AutoLateDeduction = _editCalc.AutoLateDeduction;
        Calc.AbsenceDeduction = _editCalc.AbsenceDeduction;
        Calc.LateDeduction = _editCalc.LateDeduction;
        Calc.LoanDeduction = _editCalc.LoanDeduction;
        Calc.AbsenceOverrideReason = string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(_absenceOverrideReason) ? null : _absenceOverrideReason.Trim();
        Calc.LateOverrideReason = string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(_lateOverrideReason) ? null : _lateOverrideReason.Trim();
        Calc.Penalties = _editCalc.Penalties.Select(CloneDetail).ToList();
        Calc.BonusItems = _editCalc.BonusItems.Select(CloneDetail).ToList();
        Calc.SeparateBonuses = _editCalc.SeparateBonuses.Select(CloneDetail).ToList();

        await OnSaved.InvokeAsync();
        MudDialog.Close();
    }

    private void Cancel() => MudDialog.Cancel();
}
